## Data & Monetization

- **Free:** Standalone tools, siloed data, prompt vault, distribution notifications.
- **Paid tiers:** Mastering Aesthetics ($9.99/mo), Full System/AI ($19.99/mo). Data aggregation, trends, AI coach gated by subscription.
- **Data continuity:** User data must survive upgrade; schema supports siloed (free) and integrated (paid) access.

## Tech Stack (per docs)

- **Frontend:** iOS native (SwiftUI) — docs specify iOS; implementations may use Expo/React Native.
- **Backend:** Node.js (Express) or Python (FastAPI); PostgreSQL; USDA/Edamam for food DB.
- **Notifications:** FCM/APNS for distribution alerts.

## Key Conventions

1. **Prompt Vault:** Copy-to-clipboard is primary action; source link above prompt text.
2. **Rest Timer:** Toggle per set; recommended duration by exercise; push notification on completion.
3. **TMLSN Split:** At least one complete pre-loaded workout plan required.
4. **Unit handling:** Metric (g, kg, mL) and US (oz, lbs, cups, tsp/tbsp).
